## Solution

Contacted Sitecore Support and eventually after a few back and forth, we realized that the path at which the Express Migration Tool resides in do matter.

My original path of the tool was definitely more than 260 chars.

Hence, moved it to C:\ and with only 1 sublevel, the tool now works and am able to proceed.
